<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 09:11:51 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>西门子高管表示，随着经济繁荣，西门子对印度寄予厚望</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/siemens-has-high-hopes-india-economy-booms-executive-says-2024-03-06/</link><description>西门子董事会成员马蒂亚斯·雷贝利乌斯(Matthias Rebellius)表示，西门子对其在印度的前景“非常乐观”，因为该国经济蓬勃发展，并提供了摆脱中国业务多元化的机会。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 09:04:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/siemens-has-high-hopes-india-economy-booms-executive-says-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，摩根士丹利因市场暴跌而削减了9%的中国基金部门员工</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/morgan-stanley-cuts-9-china-fund-unit-staff-amid-market-rout-sources-say-2024-03-06/</link><description>两位直接了解情况的人士表示，摩根士丹利已解雇其在中国的资产管理业务部门约 9% 的员工，因为中国不断上涨的股市削弱了其 3.8 万亿美元基金部门的前景。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 08:03:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/morgan-stanley-cuts-9-china-fund-unit-staff-amid-market-rout-sources-say-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>国家规划师称中国2024年5%的增长目标是可以实现的</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-step-up-economic-policy-adjustments-2024-state-planner-says-2024-03-06/</link><description>国家计委负责人周三表示，中国2024年5%左右的增长目标符合中国经济潜力，同时宣布计划加大政策调整和发行特别国债的力度。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 08:00:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-step-up-economic-policy-adjustments-2024-state-planner-says-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾总统表示，南海碰撞不是援引与美国防务条约的理由</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-china-sea-collision-not-reason-invoke-defence-treaty-with-us-says-2024-03-06/</link><description>菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯周三表示，最近菲律宾和中国船只在南海发生的相撞事件不是援引与美国共同防御条约的时机或理由。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 07:26:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-china-sea-collision-not-reason-invoke-defence-treaty-with-us-says-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>东盟和澳大利亚呼吁停止在南海破坏稳定的行动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asean-australia-call-an-end-destabilising-actions-south-china-sea-2024-03-06/</link><description>周三，澳大利亚和东盟在为期三天的峰会结束时发表联合声明，称所有国家都应避免在南海采取危及争议地区和平、安全与稳定的单方面行动。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 06:39:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asean-australia-call-an-end-destabilising-actions-south-china-sea-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>总统称斯里兰卡承诺在2027年至2042年期间偿还债务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/sri-lanka-committed-repaying-debt-within-2027-2042-schedule-president-says-2024-03-06/</link><description>斯里兰卡总统拉尼尔·维克勒马辛哈周三表示，斯里兰卡致力于在2027年至2042年的时间表内偿还债务，并补充说，成功的债务重组谈判将使年度外债支付额降至GDP的4%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 06:26:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/sri-lanka-committed-repaying-debt-within-2027-2042-schedule-president-says-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国能否同时保持增长和“转型”经济？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/can-china-maintain-growth-transform-its-economy-same-time-2024-03-06/</link><description>中国总理李强的国家愿景存在一个内在的矛盾：他“转变”经济模式的目标可能与保持增长率稳定在5%左右不相容。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 06:14:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/can-china-maintain-growth-transform-its-economy-same-time-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>对西方白酒制造商来说，挑战中国国酒是一项艰巨的任务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/lifestyle/challenging-chinas-national-drink-is-tall-order-western-liquor-makers-2024-03-06/</link><description>寻求利用中国年轻饮酒者对威士忌和干邑白兰地日益增长的需求的全球饮料巨头在与中国主导白酒生产商的竞争中面临着挑战。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 06:11:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/lifestyle/challenging-chinas-national-drink-is-tall-order-western-liquor-makers-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾称中国在南海“故意挑起事端”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-china-deliberately-stirring-up-trouble-south-china-sea-2024-03-06/</link><description>菲律宾周三指责中国在南海“故意挑起事端”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 05:38:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-china-deliberately-stirring-up-trouble-south-china-sea-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示，由于工厂陷入困境，中国一月至二月出口可能放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-exports-likely-slowed-jan-feb-factories-struggle-2024-03-06/</link><description>路透周三的一项调查显示，中国一月至二月的出口增长可能放缓，这表明制造商仍在为海外买家而苦苦挣扎，并需要国内进一步的政策支持。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 05:36:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-exports-likely-slowed-jan-feb-factories-struggle-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚对南海破坏稳定的行为表示担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/australia-concerned-about-destabilising-behaviour-south-china-sea-2024-03-06/</link><description>周三，中国和菲律宾船只在争议海域发生冲突的第二天，澳大利亚总理安东尼·阿尔巴内塞表示，澳大利亚非常担心南海的不安全和破坏稳定的行为。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 05:29:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/australia-concerned-about-destabilising-behaviour-south-china-sea-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>瓦努阿图警方在美国海岸警卫队的协助下称中国船只违反了捕鱼法</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/vanuatu-police-aided-by-us-coast-guard-say-chinese-vessels-violated-fishing-laws-2024-03-06/</link><description>瓦努阿图警方和官员表示，当地警方对六艘中国渔船进行检查后，发现六艘中国渔船违反了瓦努阿图的渔业法。这些渔船是第一艘在瓦努阿图海域巡逻的美国海岸警卫队船只。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 04:58:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/vanuatu-police-aided-by-us-coast-guard-say-chinese-vessels-violated-fishing-laws-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>病毒爆发后中国禁止从格鲁吉亚进口绵羊和山羊</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/china-bans-imports-sheep-goats-georgia-after-virus-outbreak-2024-03-06/</link><description>3月2日，海关总署发布公告称，因格鲁吉亚爆发绵羊、山羊痘疫情，中国暂停从格鲁吉亚进口绵羊、山羊及其相关产品。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 04:45:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/china-bans-imports-sheep-goats-georgia-after-virus-outbreak-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国投资者涌向海外 境外投资触及上限</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinese-investors-rush-abroad-hitting-outbound-investment-limit-2024-03-06/</link><description>中国资金正以极快的速度涌入投资离岸资产的基金，这与境外投资限制相抵触，并使北京方面振兴国内市场和稳定人民币的努力变得更加复杂。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 02:51:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinese-investors-rush-abroad-hitting-outbound-investment-limit-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国比亚迪在巴西建设生产基地</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-starts-construction-manufacturing-complex-brazil-2024-03-06/</link><description>中国电动汽车巨头比亚迪周三向路透社证实，该公司已开始在巴西建设生产基地。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 02:44:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-starts-construction-manufacturing-complex-brazil-2024-03-06/</guid></item></channel></rss>